TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {79231=Smith was able to motor the Jets down the field on their first drive of the second quarter, with his 13-yard scramble on 3rd-and-8 highlighting a 13-play march and setting up Folk for a 43-yard field goal. The rookie made some mistakes, however, on his next two series., 78112=The march was sparked after the Bucs' Leonard Johnson was called for a holding penalty on what would have been a Jets three-and-out.
